> Hi!
>
> Applications are invited for Core Members of the Student Election
> Commission, IIT Madras.
>
> The Student Election Commission is a constitutional body that has the
> mandate to conduct student elections in our institute. Student Members of
> the Student Election Commission report directly to the Chief and Deputy
> Election Officers and are in charge of ensuring that all election related
> rules and procedures are implemented. Furthermore, improving student
> participation in Elections is also one of the goals of this body.
>
> Students interested in being part of the commission are requested to
> answer the following questions and send in their application by the 17th =
of
> August to speaker@smail.iitm.ac.in
>
> 1. Why do you want to be part of SEC?
> 2. What are the different initiatives that can be undertaken to improve
> participation in elections?
> 3. What were the positives and drawbacks of the elections conducted in th=
e
> year 2015-16?
>
> Feel free to mail me in case of any queries.
>
> Cheers!
